    <h2>Built by the Community, for the Community</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>
      GatherPack is shaped by the experiences and feedback of real teams, volunteers, and organizers who rely on it every day. 
      Instead of being designed in isolation, its features and workflows are continually refined by people who understand the challenges of managing dynamic, people-powered groups. 
      This community-driven approach ensures that GatherPack remains practical, intuitive, and responsive to the evolving needs of organizations of all sizes.
    </p>

    <p>
      Unlike many tools that focus on static membership lists or simple communication, GatherPack is built to support the complex needs of more active organizations: 
      tracking participation, managing finances, coordinating events, and empowering leaders. 
      Its flexibility means it adapts as your group grows or changes, rather than forcing you to fit into a rigid mold.
    </p>

    <p>
      The platform is free and open source, so anyone with technical skills can deploy and customize it for their own group. 
      For those who prefer a turnkey solution, hosting, support, and custom development are available through our founder's company, 
      <a href="https://sledgehammerinfosystems.com" target="_blank">Sledgehammer Infosystems</a>. 
      Whether you're a small club or a large nonprofit, GatherPack is built to help your community thrive.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

